I'm a full-stack developer at an advertising agency in New Orleans, LA.

In my day job, I primarily work with WordPress, Expression Engine, and a custom GluePHP/PHP-ActiveRecord/Savant3|Handlebars framework.

I run a side-business called Send To My Cloud, that allows users to create a webpage where their users can upload content directly into their dropbox. https://SendToMyCloud.com.

I run another successful side-business called Private Forms, that allows users to create webforms, with PGP-encrypted submissions. https://PrivateForms.com.

I also curate the Artpacks.org Archive, a History of PC ANSI & ASCII Art, from 1990-present. http://artpacks.org

Some other projects I've written:

  http://aboutbrowser.com - A troubleshooting tool that allows users to *easily* share their browser info (version, plugins, features & CSS capabilities) with developers.
